Please apply online at - www.cafezupas.com!<br>
<br>
Our Passion<br>
Care is the secret ingredient in everything we do at Cafe Zupas! We understand, that PEOPLE make the difference! When you come in to Cafe Zupas, you immediately notice that we're different! We start with cheerful, hard-working employees, who are passionate about delivering exceptional service to everyone they meet. Our atmosphere is inviting and designed to give our guests an experience that they love to come back to.  What makes the food taste so good? We use the freshest ingredients and chef-crafted recipes! We don't just serve it the right way, we make it the right way using chopping, simmering, stirring and dipping everything from scratch! We take pride in every product we serve, it's how we have won Utah " Best of State" awards every year since 2006!  The Utah Restaurant Association recognized Café Zupas with its Best New Concept Award for 2014. "The award goes to a restaurant concept that has the growth potential to expand nationally", according to a press release quoting Kelly Christenson, chairman of the URA's board of directors. We value a fun work environment that will nurture future leaders within our organization, the growth opportunities are limitless! We aim to grow our units by 30% each year for the next 10 years, and that is only achievable with the help of ambitious employees who are as goal driven as we are! We have:<br>
a Fun Atmosphere<br>
Competitive Wages<br>
Closed Sundays<br>
Products to be Proud of<br>
Growth Opportunity<br>
Excellent Management & Leadership<br>
    </section>

